org.drip.dynamics.hjm

Class MultiFactorVolatility

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.drip.dynamics.hjm.MultiFactorVolatility
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    LognormalLIBORVolatility

    public class MultiFactorVolatility
extends java.lang.Object
    MultiFactorVolatility implements the Volatility of the Multi-factor Stochastic Evolutionary Process. The Factors may come from the Underlying Stochastic Variables, or from Principal Components.
    Author:
    Lakshmi Krishnamurthy
